plit &gt; Hvar &gt; Dubrovnik &gt; Zagreb</blockquote><br />\n我就8月頭 Budapest &gt; zagreb (開始自駕） &gt; 十六湖 &gt; zadar &gt; sibenik &gt; krka park &gt; split &gt; dubrovnik.  全部十五日   結論係唔好暑假去  一來人多又貴  二來個太陽好曬  差不多日日3x 度    如果唔自駕比較辛苦</blockquote><br />\n我係同你相反，我還車後搭火車去budapest繼續行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298d5b7568f02ce4f4e9c229a266ef438ff0a1e2","tid":496214,"uid":33961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:41:13.000Z","msg":"之前去年尾去左9日<br />\n<br />\n由Zagreb 開始玩到落Dubrovnik 上山倒數, 中間入埋Mostar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主有時間既話可以去埋黑山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b356d570b2047e2efe897715561ee18741c35c","tid":496214,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下去克羅地亞, 搭卡塔爾<br />\nHKG =&gt;QATAR (轉機) =&gt; Zagreb  (轉機) =&gt; Dubrovnik<br />\nZagreb =&gt;QATAR (轉機) =&gt; hkg<br />\n<br />\n五千五百蚊, 抵唔抵?</blockquote><br />\n正常假"},{"pid":"c910c9f926ef5db7ee6ead5dfeb8282c535a94e9","tid":496214,"uid":46192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去年尾去左9日<br />\n<br />\n由Zagreb 開始玩到落Dubrovnik 上山倒數, 中間入埋Mostar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主有時間既話可以去埋黑山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係跟LOCAL TOUR 去Mostar??<br />\n其實我諗住抄Blog 友d 行程, 廢時諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4729168a17826a7d634939e6e4006d4d7452c831","tid":496214,"uid":62423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"我前幾年復活節時段去咗20日<br />\nZagreb -&gt; 16湖 -&gt; Zadar -&gt; Split -&gt; Dubrovnik<br />\n中間有幾日搭船去d島仔day trip"},{"pid":"32f8b14cb188ab1e394340d2ac5e442afd85c6fc","tid":496214,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"